                            <comment id="17643137" author="bereng" created="Mon, 5 Dec 2022 06:55:44 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;I have been thinking instances where we would be parsing 3rd party provided yaml config files and I don&apos;t think we have any. CI for 4.0 seems to have a failure around compression but it can&apos;t be related to this change. The other are known flakies. LGTM +1&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="17643433" author="brandon.williams" created="Mon, 5 Dec 2022 16:12:44 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Committed, thanks for the review!&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
